text: @gaeliclass149 What happened to “we are the soldiers of the pandemic”.  Soldiers don’t just give up.  No matter how tough things may get.  We chose our paths   You want to be a hero or someone that could have been a hero...  now you’re getting a glimpse of what “soldier” means
